  "keyFeatures": [
    "Document authoring with Markdown and JSON using Typst and LaTeX rendering engines",
    "Content Types (document variants) with custom fields, layouts, themes, and approval flows",
    "Automated document generation pipelines triggered by form submissions",
    "Multi-stage approval workflows with role-based state transitions",
    "Electronic signatures via DocuSign and Documenso integrations",
    "AI-powered document extraction, suggestion, and refinement agents",
    "Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) with fine-grained permissions per resource",
    "Webhooks and API keys for third-party integrations",
    "Self-hosted deployment via Docker Compose with MinIO, PostgreSQL, and Typesense",
    "Version history, audit logs, and document collaboration support"
  ],
